      <ing>
        <amt>
          <qty>Date:</qty>
          <unit/></amt>
        <item>Thu, 18 Jul 1996 23:09:34 +0000</item></ing></ingredients>
    <directions>
      <step>  Combine all ingredients in a jar with a tight-fitting lid.  Shake to
  combined thoroughly.  Makes enough for 12 (2 T) servings.  Place in a hot
  cup of coffee.
  
